## ğŸ“Š API Endpoints Summary

### Posts (Existing - Working)
- `GET /api/posts` âœ…
- `POST /api/posts` âœ…
- `PUT /api/posts/{id}` âœ…
- `DELETE /api/posts/{id}` âœ…

### Groups (Existing - Working)
- `GET /api/groups` âœ…
- `POST /api/groups` âœ…
- `PUT /api/groups/{id}` âœ…
- `DELETE /api/groups/{id}` âœ…

### Roster (NEW - Now Working!)
- `GET /api/roster/shifts` âœ… List with filters
- `POST /api/roster/shifts` âœ… Create shift
- `GET /api/roster/shifts/{id}` âœ… Get shift
- `PUT /api/roster/shifts/{id}` âœ… Update shift
- `DELETE /api/roster/shifts/{id}` âœ… Delete shift
- `POST /api/roster/generate` âœ… Generate roster
- `GET /api/roster/validate` âœ… Validate EWTD
- `POST /api/roster/import-csv` âœ… Import from CSV

